      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content-step.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": true,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Quick Start Guide",
        "text": "<h2>Quick Start Guide</h2><p>[wistia_video]</p><p>To get started with your first treatment, you'll need the following:</p><ul><li>Micro-Infusion Device</li><li>1 sterile needle head</li><li>Micro-Infusion serum</li></ul><p>Ensure your hands are clean before and during the treatment and do not rush yourself.</p>"
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_image_block_QJD6bj": {
      "type": "n_guide-content-image-block",
      "blocks": {
        "image_jBYKYF": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/mi_bottle_detail.webp"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "image_jBYKYF"
      ],
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content-image-block.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Learn About Your Device",
        "text": "<h2>Learn About Your Device</h2><p>Qure's Micro-Infusion device uses 24K gold plated needles to deliver concentrated serum directly below the surface of your skin.</p><p>The needles are thinner than a strand of hair, so the treatment feels gentle — but the results are powerful.</p><p>[image]</p><p><strong>It works in two ways:</strong></p><ol><li>It triggers your skin's natural repair response for smoother and firmer looking skin.</li><li> Its 0.5 mm needles creates tiny, invisible channels in the surface of your skin and infuses the serum of your choice (for Wrinkles / for Dark Spots) directly below the skin barrier, accelerating absorption of active ingredients for faster results.</li></ol>"
      }
    },
